<article id="post-59" class="post-59 page type-page status-publish hentry">
    <header class="entry-header">
        <h1 class="entry-title">Home</h1>
    </header><!-- .entry-header -->

    <div class="entry-content">
        <p>Hello and welcome! This is a small website to organize my academic and professional work. I earned my PhD at Stony Brook University and will start as an Assistant Professor of Sociology at SUNY Geneseo beginning fall 2014.</p>
<p><span style="line-height: 1.5;">Some of the resources available on this site:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><a style="line-height: 1.5;" title="Research" href="http://restivo.info/?page_id=84">research and publications</a></li>
<li><a style="line-height: 1.5;" title="Teaching" href="http://restivo.info/?page_id=96">materials for courses I teach</a></li>
<li><a style="line-height: 1.5;" title="Recent" href="http://restivo.info/?page_id=154">recent scholarly activities</a></li>
<li><a style="line-height: 1.5;" title="Contact" href="http://restivo.info/?page_id=128">professional contact info</a></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
